{"tid":989628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵西九龍站爆玻璃幕牆　碎片險墮內地離境大堂","createTime":"2019-01-21T04:13:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T05:05:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b840de8f16aa0fa54d7b44bdc7758a045e289bc1","tid":989628,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/photo/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190121120646\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190121120646&h=602f582d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/photo/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190121120646\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190121120646&h=e10a3d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/photo/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_05p.jpg?20190121120646\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001_05p.jpg%3F20190121120646&h=51376f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高鐵香港西九龍站發生爆玻璃事件。今早(21日)6時許，有東網讀者指西九龍站B2樓層一食店外，一塊約8呎乘5呎的玻璃幕牆突然爆裂，整塊玻璃呈網狀裂開，但未有碎開分離，職員發現後立即將附近圍起，因玻璃幕牆對落為B3樓層的候車大堂，屬內地範圍。職員亦通知內地人員將B3大堂局部圍封。 <br />\n<br />\n東網記者今早到現場了解，見到工程人員拿出圖紙並仔細檢查玻璃，正勘察該玻璃碎裂情況，以確定其碎裂原因，工程人員未有回應記者提問。東網正向港鐵了解事件。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190121%2Fbkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001.html&d=K1wQF2C3TgDSVQymfi9B2AEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=396a43a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190121/bkn-20190121101010021-0121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3356840c0d9fdc18003e0ceff2b313d198018f4","tid":989628,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:05:20.000Z","msg":"反攻大陸？"}]}